om where you want light. But there are many other uses. Some people with kids put these on window unit air conditioners in rarely used rooms, so they aren’t constantly nagging them to turn things off.</p><p>Or, despite cats’ contempt for human life, many people keep them as pets. When cats use litter boxes, they produce undesirable smells. You can connect an air purifier to one of these to automatically turn on and remove those smells.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F277d507a-8dd3-4374-8331-19abc06af546_500x294.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/eP__lzO5MlYEwJcXPzl3DrFu_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/OMT1Sqdrl8eVJN-CMsBIKwyRcrDo96RKImFU6_Mhojo=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYyNzdkNTA3YS04ZGQzLTQzNzQtODMzMS0xOWFiYzA2YWY1NDZfNTAweDI5NC5qcGVn 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/9MK_ 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/ZgiXRc5aA0T8qatH_kMWM3YU5_6NJbfoyq-TYr1-pD4=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMjc3ZDUwN2EtOGRkMy00Mzc0LTgzMzEtMTlhYmMwNmFmNTQ2XzUwMHgyOTQuanBlZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Jdz8eLuecHQ2_b4y5mmX_" width="264" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/d3_wWgq-5gTe89FMIEiabyslOQAL7V_RCvGFvxLpDYk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZ