 or find mechanical timers too beautiful and intuitive and bulletproof. ($15)</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff848a23c-b57c-44bd-92be-cc66082c7f9c_500x275.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/cir05VRu25GFxiFG4x3xD_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/QwPPTZAPOpVYfY3GMbuivXVvTtHe98svLCqeV-7VY40=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjg0OGEyM2MtYjU3Yy00NGJkLTkyYmUtY2M2NjA4MmM3ZjljXzUwMHgyNzUuanBlZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/uJ1Tl1wgiNEbmpF0rvTT9JLagWpIpfjX-gABvMYjzMk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGZjg0OGEyM2MtYjU3Yy00NGJkLTkyYmUtY2M2NjA4MmM3ZjljXzUwMHgyNzUuanBlZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." width="274" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/R0bXKInGtWYh6admdch9wvVLAL7Mf4RpLpk_5I_-x3U=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmODQ4YTIzYy1iNTdjLTQ0YmQtOTJiZS1jYzY2MDgyYzdmOWNfNTAweDI3NS5qcGVn 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/jq_7aCA0qXipKvXsCd_0c4H- 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/B3HFUncDRQwPH21mf4_DcY7ZLs7ht51V_QXEsEVJhhs=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS